trans-unit.source: The DirSyncResponseControl class is a directory control used to pass DirSyncRequest information from the server to the client.
trans-unit.target: DirSyncResponseControl 类是用来从服务器到客户端传递 DirSyncRequest 信息的目录控件。

trans-unit.source: The Cookie property contains an opaque structure returned by the directory.
trans-unit.target: Cookie 属性包含目录由返回的不透明结构。

trans-unit.source: This property is updated by the directory during each <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest>, which enables the control to incrementally read changes from the directory.
trans-unit.target: 此属性在每个过程更新目录<xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest>，从而使控件能够以增量方式从目录读取更改。</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest>

trans-unit.source: An opaque structure returned by the directory.
trans-unit.target: 返回由目录的不透明结构。

trans-unit.source: The MoreData property specifies whether there is more data to return.
trans-unit.target: MoreData 属性指定是否要返回的详细数据。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if there is more data; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, otherwise.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果没有更多的数据;<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>，否则为。

trans-unit.source: The ResultSize property specifies the size of the result.
trans-unit.target: ResultSize 属性指定的结果的大小。
